"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-4US","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":866,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/06\/14\/fi-dunya-hasana\/","url_meta":{"origin":18902,"position":0},"title":"Hadith of Akhirah: Give us good in this life, in Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would say, \u201cOur Lord, grant us good in this world and good in the Hereafter and save us from the punishment of the Hellfire.\u201d (2:201) Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 4522, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2690 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3685,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/14\/save-yourself-hellfire-date\/","url_meta":{"origin":18902,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Save yourself from Hell, even with small charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Adi ibn Hatim reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGuard\u00a0yourself against the Hellfire, even with half of a date in charity. If one cannot find it, then with a kind word.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6540, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1016 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38783,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/13\/righteous-intercede\/","url_meta":{"origin":18902,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Intercession: Righteous intercede for sinful brethren","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 13, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBy the One in whose hand is my soul, none among you are more fervent to claim a right from Allah on the Day of Resurrection than the believers on behalf of their brothers in the Hellfire.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3791,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/24\/muslim-who-fasts-distant-hellfire\/","url_meta":{"origin":18902,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: A Muslim who fasts will be distant from Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\"Whoever fasts a day in the way of Allah, Allah will move his face away from the Hellfire by a distance of seventy years.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2840, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1153 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonli